extendedInfo.description: The Movement of Change Book ExperienceThis special book App profiles authors who all have a mission to create change in the world with their message.  The app will give you an extensive sample of their message through a sample chapter, an audio or video clip, workbook questions that you answer on your phone, access to additional online content, and information about the authors and their books.  This App will feel like a digital workshop with a wide range of content topics and Messengers of Change.  And... it's free!
